PRIVACY NOTICE:

This software is designed to process sensitive personal data entirely on your
local device. The authors make no warranties about the security of your data
and recommend:

1. Using full-disk encryption on your device
2. Using strong passwords/authentication
3. Keeping your system updated
4. Backing up your encryption keys securely
5. Not using this software on shared or public computers

The software does not transmit data to external servers (except to localhost
Ollama if configured). However, the authors are not responsible for any data
breaches, loss, or unauthorized access to your information.

USE AT YOUR OWN RISK.
